# Project Structure

## Key Files and Directories

### App Routes
- [app/chat.tsx](mdc:src/app/chat.tsx) - Client-side chat implementation with `useChat`
- [app/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx) - Server-side main page
- [app/api/chat/route.ts](mdc:src/app/api/chat/route.ts) - API route for chat implementation

### Core Files
- [models.ts](mdc:src/models.ts) - Model declarations
- [serper.ts](mdc:src/serper.ts) - Serper implementation
- [types.ts](mdc:src/types.ts) - Shared types
- [utils.ts](mdc:src/utils.ts) - Utility functions

### Database
- [server/db/schema.ts](mdc:src/server/db/schema.ts) - Drizzle schema definitions
- [server/db/queries.ts](mdc:src/server/db/queries.ts) - Database helper functions

### Authentication
- [server/auth/index.ts](mdc:src/server/auth/index.ts) - Next-auth powered authentication

### Configuration
- [.env](mdc:.env) - Environment variables
- [env.js](mdc:src/env.js) - Type-safe environment variable validation

## Package Management
- Use `pnpm` as the package manager
- Run `pnpm run db:push` after making changes to the database schema
